title: Philips Sonicare DiamondClean electric toothbrush Pink Edition - whiter, healthier teeth for life
description:
The new Philips Sonicare DiamondClean electric toothbrush Pink Edition 
makes your smile as brilliant as you feel. It removes up 
to 100% more stains, and 7 times more plaque, than an 
manual toothbrush. Its award-winning design enables 
you to charge it by simply placing the toothbrush in its 
glass. Or, if you’re on the move, its innovative charging 
case connects to your computer by USB. No matter 
where you go you’ll always get a cleaner white, with pink.

asset.author: Philips

transcripts: I love to travel almost as much as I love staying home. Either way a few things stay the same. I eat healthy food so I feel my best and I always have my Philips Sonicare Diamond Clean Pink on me so I look my best. Of course is not always about having a glowing smile. Having healthier gums and cleaner teeth fine tuned to my needs are important too. With a USB travel case and glass charger for home and a long lasting battery There is no where my Philips Sonicare and I won't go. For the whitest brightest smile where ever I go. Innovation and you. Philips Sonicare.
